<lg xml:id="t.6.1.01.160" type="proverb" n="1.160"><p xml:id="t6101.p150" n="43-44" corresp="c6101.D.1.160.43">
<note lang="eng">cf. <xref doc="t.6.1.14" from="t.6.1.14.39">6.1.14.39</xref></note>
Marrying is human. Having children is divine.</p></lg>
<lg xml:id="t.6.1.01.161" type="proverb" n="1.161"><p xml:id="t6101.p151" n="45-46" corresp="c6101.D.1.161.45">
…… born …… superior …….</p></lg>
<lg xml:id="t.6.1.01.162" type="proverb" n="1.162"><p xml:id="t6101.p152" n="47" corresp="c6101.D.1.162.47">
