<lg xml:id="t.6.1.01.166" type="proverb" n="1.166"><p xml:id="t6101.p156" n="53-54" corresp="c6101.D.1.166.53">
At the top it is a wild cow, at the bottom it is a fish. At the top it is shattered potsherds, at the bottom it is half a cubit.</p></lg>
<lg xml:id="t.6.1.01.167" type="proverb" n="1.167"><p xml:id="t6101.p157" n="55-56" corresp="c6101.D.1.167.55">
<note lang="eng">cf. <xref doc="t.6.1.07" from="t.6.1.07.22">6.1.07.22</xref></note>
I visit it by day, I visit it at nightfall. I always stand by the lamentation drum!</p></lg>
